title: Juul Franssen
text:
Juul Franssen (born 18 January 1990) is a Dutch <a href="judoka">judoka</a>.
She participated at the <a href="2018%20World%20Judo%20Championships">2018 World Judo Championships</a>, winning a bronze medal.
In 2020, she won one of the bronze medals in the <a href="2020%20European%20Judo%20Championships%20%E2%80%93%20Women%27s%2063%20kg">women's 63 kg</a> event at the <a href="2020%20European%20Judo%20Championships">2020 European Judo Championships</a> held in Prague, Czech Republic.
